summary: This mod removes all the green from the walls of Solitude.
descriptionHtml:
Are you tired of Solitude looking like a overgrown ruin? All the slippery moss on the walls, the ivy that weakens the structures?

Then have a look at this.

A team of dedicated, bored housecarls was called in with a simple mission: to clean the walls of the city! This tiny mod is the result of their hard work. It removes all the moss, ivy, vines and clovers from the walls of Solitude\'s structures.
author: Dragten
